comment: /**  * Does this parameter support a ResultSet, i.e. does it hold a  * ResultSetExtractor, RowCallbackHandler or RowMapper?  */
code: /**  * Does this parameter support a ResultSet, i.e. does it hold a  * ResultSetExtractor, RowCallbackHandler or RowMapper?  */ public boolean isResultSetSupported() {     return (this.resultSetExtractor != null || this.rowCallbackHandler != null || this.rowMapper != null). }
